Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%post
    set -e

    # Update package index and install Python tooling
    apt-get update
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3-pip
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # ---------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Create the initial directory structure and seed the users.log file
    # ---------------------------------------------------------------------
    mkdir -p /home/user/data
    chmod 0777 /home/user/data   # Allow the runtime (non-root) user to write here

    cat > /home/user/data/users.log <<'EOF'
alice
bob
charlie
alice
bob
alice
dave
eve
bob
charlie
charlie
charlie
frank
grace
heidi
ivan
judy
mallory
oscar
peggy
trent
victor
walter
peggy
trent
trent
trent
mallory
mallory
trent
EOF

    # Ensure correct permissions on the log file (read-only for others)
    chmod 0644 /home/user/data/users.log

%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author  ChatGPT
    Description  Starter image for username frequency report task (users.log preset, pytest installed)

%help
    This container provides the initial environment for the “username frequency
    report” task.  It includes:
      • /home/user/data/users.log  – the raw log the student must process
      • pytest                    – pre-installed for test execution